Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,简 这早午餐真绝了\NJane, this brunch is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 有么 我只是看了一些烹饪博客\NOh, please. I was just reading some cooking blogs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,又参考了美食网站然后就 嗯\Nand got a little epicurious and decided to just, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,把东西乱七八糟地一煮 来点核桃糖?\Nthrow together whatever looked fun. Candied walnut?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的太好吃了 全是你自己做的?\NThese are fantastic. Did you make 'em yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,简单的不能再简单了\NCouldn't have been easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需敲开 弄个小孔 烤一下\NYou just crack 'em, hole 'em, toast 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,再用橄榄油那么一抹\Nbrush 'em with a little bit of olive oil,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把他们和辣椒粉姜粉\Nthen rub 'em with cayenne pepper, some turmeric
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,肉桂糖一起搅拌 放进烤箱\Nand some cinnamon sugar, and you put 'em in the oven
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快速烘烤 每五分钟翻一次\Nfor a quick roast, flipping them every five minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,总共一个半小时 -我说你这是要飙泪么?\Nfor... an hour and a half. - Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有点 我快累死了\NA little bit. I am just so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们 我不想总是成为\NGuys, I hate to be the girl that, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大家谈话的焦点\Nmakes every conversation about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但说实话 -你就是\Nbut let's be honest. - You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是滴 我今天晚上要去相亲\NYeah, I am. I'm going on a blind date tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对方是听起来超赞的的 罗杰\Nwith the most amah-zing sounding guy, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还有人叫罗杰?\NAre people still named Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你得把这个推了 今天晚上你和我一起出去\NYou gotta cancel it. You have a date tonight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸妈来了\NMy parents are in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你都做了我三年的女朋友了\NYou're my girlfriend of three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.91,0:00:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,晕 我把他们进城这事忘得一干二净\NOh, my God. I totally forgot they were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我不能再做你的假女友了\NI'm so sorry. I can't be your beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说去跟陌生人约会来得\NYou're telling me that one single date with some stranger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,比咱俩之间虚假的感情更重要?\Nis more important to you than what we fake have?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 而且说实话 我再不想做你的挡箭牌了\NYeah, and honestly, I'm sick of being your beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你完全不像个同志\NI mean, for someone who behaves nothing like a gay guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但你装直男装的也太不像了吧\Nyou have even less of an idea how to act like a straight guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这一对 怎么样?真是无限享受啊\NHow about these things, huh? Can't get enough of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的对吧?耶!\NAm I right? Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你又接着说"更别说这块地方里的乐事了\NAnd then you followed it with "and don't even get me started
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-那我怎么办?\N"with what's going on down there." - So what am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你应该勇敢出柜\NMaybe you should come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 出柜这种行为太GAY了，再说也没必要\NUgh. Coming out is so gay. And why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸妈两年才来一次\NMy parents only visit, like, once every two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我可以做你的假女友哦 但我要叫拉丽莎\NHey, wait. I can be your beard, but I wanna be named Larissa,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我要做个雕刻家 -简 你能帮我不?\Nand I'm a... Sculptress. - Jane, will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么找我? -为什么不找我?\NWhy me? - Why not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 你是我唯一的希望 -我说我可以啊\NPlease, you're my only hope. - I just offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,简 其他人都帮不了我了\NJane, there is no one else that can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 为啥没人理我?当我不存在? -是滴\NWait. Can nobody hear me? Am I ghost? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不是针对你 我只是觉得\NIt's nothing personal. I just personally feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,简会做的更好 -这还不叫针对我?\Nthat Jane would be better at it. - How is that not personal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.12,0:01:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这倒是，扮同志的女友我绝对一流的\NIt's true. I'd be an awesome beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,父母们都喜欢我 -那么你答应了?\NParents love me. - So you'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不 马科斯 是时候你该向他们出柜了\NNo, Max. It's time for you to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,简说的对 -好了，我知道你们啥意思了\NJane's right. - Look, I hear you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,阿莱克斯 你帮我不?\NAlex, will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没门！我都说了三遍了你却当面羞辱了我\NNo! I offered three times and you insulted me to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为我以为我可以找到更好的人选啊\NIt's only 'cause I thought I had someone better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说...\NI mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:02:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HB76C22&}幸福终点站\N第一季  第04集\N==深影字幕组==
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真不知道在七点之前我该去哪找个完美的女孩\NSo I don't know where I'm gonna find a perfect girl
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当挡箭牌 -嘿 我有个疯狂的想法\Nto play a beard by 7:00. - Hey, I got a crazy thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你想穿裙子抹口红化身成性感兔女郎?\NPut you in a dress and lipstick like sexy bugs bunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你个傻逼\NIdiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对你的父母出柜吧 不会太糟糕的\NCome out to your parents. It won't be that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是和蔼开明的犹太人\NThey're sweet liberal Jews.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,首先 你根本不知道他们会如何反应\NFirst of all, you never know how they're gonna react.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,其次 他们超想抱孙子\NSecond of all, they're obsessed with grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我告诉他们 我没法要孩子\NHow bad are they gonna freak when I tell 'em
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一定会崩溃 -你还是可以有孩子啊\NI can't have kids? - You can still have kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,呃! 我才不想要孩子\NUgh! I don't want kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,马科斯 这都是借口 知道不?\NMax, these are just excuses. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这有点困难\NI know it's hard, but come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 兄弟 今天晚上你真的应该坦白了\NYou should tell 'em tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你一起去 给你精神支持 -真的?\NI'll come with you for moral support. - You'd do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 兄弟 因为我爱你啊\NOf course I would, buddy, 'cause I love ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是因为你知道我爸会买单吧\NPlus you know my dad's gonna pay for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我要两道开胃菜 估计还能再吃个牛排\NYeah, I'm gonna get two apps and probably a steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还有蟹肉土豆泥 -我就喜欢蟹肉土豆泥\NYeah, crab mashed potatoes. - Love me some crab mash-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信 我花了3小时\NUnbelievable. I spent three hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,却没人注意到我精心用餐巾环套好的餐巾\Nand nobody even noticed the homemade napkin rings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还是荷叶边的 -我注意到了\Nmade from rickrack. - I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?指给我看看?\NReally? Can you point to them on this table?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,何必呢?\NWhy you gotta do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不给马科斯当挡箭牌是不是有点不够意思?\NWas it wrong that I didn't wanna be Max's beard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得向父母出柜的话\NI just think he'd be so much happier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他会更快乐\Nif he were honest with his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,必须的，好奇的问一句\NYeah, totally. Just curious. Didn't it take you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是也用了半年时间才告诉你父母\Nlike, six months, before you told your parents
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你和一个黑人住一起? -这根种族没有关系\Nyou were living with a black guy? - That had nothing to do with race.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我父母不在乎肤色\NMy parents don't see color.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只关心的是谁睡了他们的女儿\NThey just see sleeping with their daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我可不仅仅是睡觉而已\NOh, I sleep the sleep out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 总之 我需要在自己准备好的时候\NI know you do. Anyway, I just needed to tell them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再告诉他们 -可是马科斯\Nin my own time. - As opposed to Max,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚就要向父母说真话\Nwho has to tell his parents he's gay tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他的异性恋朋友认为他应该这么做?\Nbecause his straight friends think he should?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那不一样 -怎么不一样?\NNo, that is totally different. - How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你何必呢?\NWhy you gotta do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 请问你是莎拉么?\NExcuse me. Are you Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我猜你不是罗杰\NNo. Oh. And I'm guessing you're not Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,现在说是的话是不是有点晚?\NIs it too late to say that I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那现在说"鸡蛋要半生的还是全熟"（指早餐）是否有点早?\NIs it too early to say, "how do you like your eggs?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我一紧张\NI'm sorry. Oh, when I get nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就变身成"黄金女郎"里的布兰奇\NI turn into Blanche from "The Golden Girls."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就是剧中的索菲亚了\NI'm a Sophia man myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 -我是道格\NOh. - I'm Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我是彭妮 那么你也在等着相亲咯?\NHi. Penny. Uh, so you're waiting for a blind date, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 可是我都等了半个多小时了\NI was, but I've been here, like, a half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我被放鸽子了 - 彭妮?彭妮 哈茨?\NI think I've been stood up. - Penny? Penny Hartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,彭妮 哈茨?\NPenny Hartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,彭妮 哈茨?\NPenny Hartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜我也被人放了鸽子...\NAnd it looks like I've been stood up, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你不打算给他一个机会?\NDid you wanna give him another minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不 -你确定?\NI'm good. - You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,确定 -好吧 要喝的么?\NYeah. - Okay. You want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 谢谢 -不客气\NYes, please. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 马科斯! 马科斯!\NOh, Max! Maxie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 马科斯 我们在这\NHey, Max. We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在这 -看见我们没?\NOver here? - You see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这! -他们没来 咱撤吧\NWe're here! - No, they're not here. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 没事的\NHey, it's gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,像个爷儿们一样告诉他们你喜欢爷儿们\NNow man up and tell 'em you like dudes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来!\NGet over here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 妈妈\NHey, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 宝贝 -嘿\NHello, sweetheart. - Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 亲爱的 -很高兴见到你\NHi, honey. - Good to see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你穿的够暖吗? - 是的 我够暖和了\NAre you warm enough? - Yes, I'm warm enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 老爹 你还好么?\NHi, dad. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 戴夫也来了 戴夫 真是个惊喜\NOh, and Dave, too. Mwah! Dave, this is such a nice surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,彭妮呢?我们可是急着见她呢\NWhere's Penny? We were so excited to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 她来不了了\NOh, she couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?\NWhy?
