Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要坐早上 6 点的飞机回去\Nand they're on, like, a 6:00 A.M. flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 呃 那真糟糕 - 是的 他们也很不爽\N- Oh, that's too bad. - Yeah, they're bummed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但你今天的表现巨赞\NBut operation beard was a huge success.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我欠你一个大人情\NI owe you big-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你什么时候想去乡村俱乐部\NIf you ever wanna get into a country club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs12\1c&H00FFFF&}{\a6}本集结尾部分的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,需要一个假的白人丈夫\Nand you're looking for, like, a fake white husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我随时恭候\NI'm your guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他们明天一大早就走\NThey're leaving early.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,天 我还很期待与他们一起逛逛\NGod, I was so looking forward to hanging out with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 我觉得你现在很脏\NNo. Feels dirty now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚度过了一个最诡异的约会\NI had the weirdest date last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我昨晚和马科斯\NOkay, I made out with Max
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在他父母面前亲热了一番\Nin front of his parents last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你的约会不可能比我的还诡异\Nso you might not wanna play weird date poker with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是决定去了? 怎么样?\NYou decided to go? How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定了 他们爱死我了 但他们很早就得走\NNailed it. They loved me. They had to leave early,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 马科斯 说他们因为不能\Nbut Max said they were devastated
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,和我多呆下而痛苦的要死\Nthey didn't get to spend more time with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗? 在我看来他们可好的很哪\NReally? 'Cause they look like they're doing okay to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 呃 我\NOh, uh... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 马科斯\NHello, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的亲娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我吓着你了吗?\NI'm sorry. Did I startle you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用道歉\NYou're not sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你一个人坐在我的公寓里还不开灯\NYou're sitting alone in my apartment in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我很确定你是故意那么做 - 我过来\N- Pretty sure you meant to do that. - I just wanted to come by,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只是想确定你父母走了没\Nmake sure your parents got off okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 那很不错 很好\NYeah. It's great. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗? 在机场没排什么长长的队伍?\NYou sure? No long lines at the terminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没晚点吗?\NNo delays?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊 你知道 都很顺利\NNo, it was smooth. You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 很好\NOh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,十分非常以及特别好 不过要在爱玛店吃早餐\NGood, good, good, 'cause there can be such a long wait
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可要排很久队的吧\Nfor a table at Emma's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，自从那次被大众点评推荐之后\NYeah, well, since that review came out, you know, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 他们还在这\NAll right, fine. They're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而且今晚才走\NThey're not leaving till tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么给我说他们走了?\NWhy did you tell me they were leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们喜欢我 - 呃\NThey loved me. - Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不喜欢我?\NThey didn't love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 恩 - 但我绝对把他们拿下了啊\N- Uh... - But I killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你不懂这词在这种情况下\NI don't think you understand what "killed" means
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,的含义\Nin this context.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有一晚  马科斯 和我第一次吵架\NSo the other night, Maxie and I got in our first fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我试着对他发火 但你们看他\Nand I tried to stay mad at him, but look at this punim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会对这张帅脸发火啊?\NHow could you stay mad at this punim?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 怎么会?\N- How could ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 让姐亲一下这张帅脸\NOoh, give me this punim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们知道，都是从这位先生这里遗传过来的\NBut you know. You know, since he gets it from this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哈? 噢 看看你\NHuh? Ooh, look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我得去上个厕所\NOh. This shiksa's gotta pish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她还学了犹太语啊\NShe's even learning yiddish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊，她可真是啥都会\NBoy, she's a keeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 我是 - 我知道 知道\N- Yes, I am. - I know, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我真受不了这女的\NI can't stand that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊? 我还以为你喜欢她\NWhat? I thought you liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我们喜欢什么?\NWhat did you think we liked?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她在公众场合和你舌了一大堆的吻?\NThe bizarre amount of time she French-kissed you in public?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,或者一直说犹太话？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这可是榜上有名的反犹太行为 - 这女孩真的很\N- on the anti-semitic. - That girl is so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 我忘了钱包 - 嘿\N- Hey! Forgot my purse. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该给你装个铃铛\NWe're gonna have to put a bell on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,噢! 叮 叮 叮 过来\NOh! Ding, ding, ding. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为是在帮你个mitzvah\NBut I thought it was doing you a mitzvah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你犹太话还没说够吗\NEnough with the yiddish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好 这件还是这件?\NOkay, this one or this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗? 我觉得你该穿裤子\NYou know what? I think you should wear pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你踢正步的时候就方便多了\NYou know? It'll give you more freedom to goose-step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不觉得那样很好笑\NI can't find that funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 别这样\NOh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我为这个谈话还专门查了"二战"的喂鸡百科呢\NI wiki'd "World War II" just for this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那你和 希特勒 今晚要做什么?\NSo what are you and Hitler gonna do tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看电影? 吃饭? 入侵波兰?\NMovie? Dinner? Invade Poland?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你说完没?\NAre you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一句 我希望他是你的真命天子\NI got one more. I hope he's Mr. Reich.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不错，等的就是这句\NGlad we waited for that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我和他出去疯了吗?\NDo you think I'm crazy, going out with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 如果我和他结婚\NI mean, if we got married,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 这就是我的未来\Nokay, this is my future...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,彭妮 希特勒 道格 和 彭妮 希特勒\NPenny Hitler, Doug and Penny Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,道格拉斯 希特勒 夫妇?\NMr. and Mrs. Douglas Hitler?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 "道格拉斯" 有点帮助吧\NOoh, the "Douglas" helps a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 为什么你不就叫 "彭妮 哈茨"呢?\NLook, why don't you just keep "Penny Hartz"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,或者用个连字符\NOr you can hyphenate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,彭妮 哈茨-希特勒\N- Penny Hartz-Hitler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，好多了\NYeah, that's a winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 如果那个人的姓氏\NCome on. If this guy's last name
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是他最差的东西 那也不算太坏\Nis the worst thing about him, that's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 他听上去也是个不错的人\NI mean, he sounds like a pretty great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗 你是对的 完全正确!\NYou know, you're right. You are right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,名字有什么关系呢?\NWhat does a name even matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 谁会在乎呢 是吧?\NI mean, who cares, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我和那个土耳其人 阿尼德 几内次也约会过\NI dated that turkish guy, Ahneed Jirnutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我喜欢他\NOh, I liked A.J.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那出什么问题了?\NWhat went wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 马科斯\NHey, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是阿莱克斯吗 或者是女雕塑家拉丽莎\NIs this Alex, or is this Larissa the sculptress
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有这个迷人的声音?\Nwith the sultry voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 简 呢? - 她沉船了\N- What happened to Jane? - She tanked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你是对的 拜托 我这次真的很需要你的帮助\NYou were right. Please, Al. I really need your help on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那才是我想听的\NThat's all I needed to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,把细节告诉我 Larissa马上就到\NJust give me the deets, and Larissa is on her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,8:30 好了\N8:30, okay..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢 呃 还能请你帮个忙吗?\NThank you so much Oh, could you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太刻意的弄些犹太的东西\NGo easy on the Jewish stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,简 试过 可是都不买账\NJane tried it... not well received.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明白\NGot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我要成为MAX的假女友了\NI am gonna be Max's beard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意帮他还真是奇怪\NSo weird you wanna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你和 希特勒 今晚过得愉快\NHave fun with Hitler tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,小心别让他对你开“炮” 嘣!\NMake sure he doesn't get in your panzer. What? Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 你为啥还有找其他人?\NDude, why do you need another beard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你父母已经认为你是个异性恋了\NYour parents already think you're straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我妈是犹太人\NYeah, my mom is Jewish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我不快点找个她喜欢的姑娘\NIf I don't find a girl that she likes soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她就会替我在她的所有朋友中\Nshe's gonna start setting me up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,找个 "风趣" 单身的女孩\Nwith all her friends' "fun" single daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么不直接出柜?\NThen why not just come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 你父母知道我是同志也没什么啊\NI mean, your parents are cool with me being gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸还一直告诉我他有多喜欢"妈妈咪呀"\NYour dad can't stop telling me how much he loves "Mamma Mia."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 可你不是他们的儿子 知道吗?\NWell, you're not their son, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还要在这待 4 个小时\NThey're here for 4 more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个方式最简单\NIt's just easier this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗? 但看上去还有很多事要做\NReally? 'Cause it seems like a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,多事?你曾经和米里亚姆 谢克特的女儿\NWork? You ever been on a 6-hour architectural tour
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,邱吉尔 有过 6 小时的建筑学旅行吗?\Nwith Miriam Schecter's daughter Chuchel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,邱吉尔 谢克特 是犹太人?\NChuchel Schecter's Jewish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,表面上是\NOnly in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.51,0:14:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么可以不喜欢我?\NHow could they not like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我喜欢你 那就足够了\NWell, I like you and that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道怎么回事了 - 又来了\N- I know what happened. - Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我太过了，可能有点太粘人\NI tried too hard. Probably came off a little needy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该去向他们展示一个轻松随和的jane\NI should go over there and show them easy, breezy Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有这样的ane吗?\NThere's an easy, breezy Jane?
